snippet.title: TEKKEN 7 - Season Pass 2 Reveal: Armor King | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Masked in mystery, Armor King rises to the ring with fearless confidence. 

Armor King will return to continue his long-standing feud with Marduk in #TEKKEN7 Season Pass 2. Order today: 
https://bandainam.co/Tekken7
